            "pre_notes": [],
            "type": "METHOD_STEP"
        },
        {
            "text": "Frying pan, add meat, and brown, adding oregano for the last few minutes",
            "post_notes": [],
            "pre_notes": [],
            "type": "METHOD_STEP"
        },
        {
